Package hu.invitech.insight.processor.sdk.v1.resource

POJO classes used by the ResourceInterface.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IncomingDataInfo
    Represents the information about incoming data produced by a resource.
    ResourceInfo
    Represents the information required to add a new resource to the processor.
    ResourceTypeInfo
    Represents the information about an available resource type.
    ResourceTypeMap
    Represents the description of all the available resource types.
    SensorTypes
    Represents the predefined sensor types that can be used to identify the data type of an IncomingDataInfo.
    ValidationInfo
    Represents data validation information
